Product description

A classic. You'll reach for it every time the wind gets blustery and the temperatures drop. Not only warm, but comfortable, too.

Our acrylic watch hat is made of stretchable, 100% acrylic rib-knit fabric for warmth and comfort. The Carhartt logo is sewn on the front of this classic, one -size-fits-all hat.

    5.0 out of 5 starsMore than adequate
    ByB Gateson January 8, 2017
    Size: One Size|Color: Brite Lime|Verified Purchase
    I have a couple of these and this last purchase is so I could throw one into my EMT bag. I will go out on a call and never know either how long I'll be on scene or what the conditions will be when I'm done. I also picked the "brite lime" color to give me a tad more visibility. (Yes, this is VERY bright) I have to say on the subject of fit, these are close to perfect as you can get with a "one size fits all." I normally have to hunt for hats of any kind as I have a XXL or even XXXL head. This actually fits me without the usually watch cap squeeze that you can get with the traditional wool ones. (also no itch) But, it also fits my size small wife's head. I also originally worried that I'd lose in the thermal/cold resistant area with the acrylic fiber, but I've been ok with these hats down to -15. I am working about 90% of the time I've been in that level of cold, but I was more than ok. I do have one of those classic "bunny ear" fur lined caps that I pull out when it gets even colder, but the difference in comfort level appears to be less than significant.
